      "Text": "Security update for libsoup",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for libsoup fixes the following issues:\n\n- A bug in the HTTP Chunked Encoding code has been fixed that could have been\n  exploited by attackers to cause a stack-based buffer overflow in client or\n  server code running libsoup (bsc#1052916, CVE-2017-2885).\n\nThis update was imported from the SUSE:SLE-12-SP2:Update update project.",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
